mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SQUARE DANCES "Allemande "Q" Break", and "Heel and Toe Square". ROUND DANCES "Glow Worm Gavotte", and "Jambalaya". SPECIAL FEATURES "That Old Time Dance", "Phrasing", and "Beginners Graduation". REGULAR FEATURES "As I See It", "Help for Your Square Dance Club", "Musician's Corner", "Women on the Square", "Square of the Month", "'Round the Outside Ring", "Green Sheet", "From the Floor", "Calendar of Square Dancing Events", "On the Road", and "Looks at Books".
